cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.HC, cs.GR, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on using ROS to control a drone through body gestures.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper uses OpenPose to process video and obtain the user's pose.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is relevant as the paper proposes a more intuitive way to control a drone through body gestures.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is possible as the paper involves visualizing the user's pose and translating it into high-level commands for the drone.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper involves processing video in real-time.
